{"tid":771950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打同我一樣都試過有啲野搵極都搵唔到，但隔一排唔搵就自己出現返呢？","createTime":"2018-08-08T11:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T17:52:03.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"653527295bb40ca2e6c2e20832f8ae7191a34083","tid":771950,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n都市人日忙夜忙<br />\n飲食又唔定時，屋企亂就自然唔願執<br />\n有時咁樣都真係好易整唔見啲野架<br />\n唔見左野果陣，唔好彩既時候真係可以搵足大半日都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係啲唔等使既野都真係無乜所謂<br />\n但如果係啲好重要好等住用又搵唔到既野<br />\n確實係會搞到人好頭痕架<br />\n<br />\n就好似我咁咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早幾日返工已經比HR個阿head鬧左鑊甘<br />\n諗住放工返到屋企可以輕鬆下啦<br />\n點知當我準備坐低喺飯檯度電視撈飯之際<br />\n居然搵極都搵唔到我果個<br />\nmyTV SUPER remote <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩TVB仲有出個myTV SUPER remote app<br />\n就算無左個實體remote<br />\n都可以透過安裝喺智能電話既應用程式<br />\n去通過Wi-Fi網絡黎連接返myTV SUPER既服務 真係貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係既話呢幾日我都收睇唔到心水既TVB節目了<br />\n<br />\n講返正題先,雖然用電話都可以當係remote係唔錯既選擇<br />\n不過呢個都只係應急方案黎啫<br />\n如果有日斷左Wi-Fi連接<br />\n無左個實體remote都係睇唔到野架<br />\n所以我頭先竟然屎坑中棍咁從雜地堆中搵返我個myTV SUPER remote出黎，真係謝天謝地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果搵唔返既話<br />\n無論我依家係用緊基本版myTV SUPER只需要780蚊就可以睇足十二個月<br />\n定係用緊至尊版myTV SUPER只需要1880蚊就可以睇足十二個月<br />\n我都應該無得再睇<br />\n又或者要打去客戶熱線查詢<br />\n問下有無得配個另一個remote<br />\n到時就真係因小失大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我想問<br />\n我岩岩又發現自己唔見左個電視機遙控<br />\n又因為我部電視機係入牆式<br />\n所以無得用手撳掣開<br />\n咁,我.......可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd839108002bd41987f182b02d5d8870f0ef1a44","tid":771950,"uid":27970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"樓主個post"},{"pid":"6bbcdb1e7ac99acd17772afe92c095cce6d5e854","tid":771950,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd839108002bd41987f182b02d5d8870f0ef1a44","tid":771950,"uid":27970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"樓主個post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6790397220e4d52bf4a3157aa4e2d276c180b796","tid":771950,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"廣告？"},{"pid":"7df0ec115bac8168338450dd1cfa1361c0d880f1","tid":771950,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6790397220e4d52bf4a3157aa4e2d276c180b796","tid":771950,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"廣告？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b2b18afd5585faf3e240d1edb1b4865afb1272","tid":771950,"uid":195815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"too long + mytv super = didn't read"}]}